# Ignore Everything by default
*

# Whitelist Folders (Main Code)
!GitHub-PR-Risk-Reviewer/
!GitHub-PR-Risk-Reviewer/*.py
!PR-Agent-Brain-Simple/
!PR-Agent-Brain-Simple/*.py
!PR-Agent-Brain-Simple/*.txt
!PR-Agent-GitHub-Writer/
!PR-Agent-GitHub-Writer/*.py

# Whitelist Documentation
!docs/
!docs/*.md
!README.md
!SETUP_GUIDE.md
!deploy.py
!requirements.txt
!*.ipynb

# Explicitly Ignore Junk inside Whitelisted Folders
*.zip
*.json
__pycache__/
*.DS_Store
